MOST IMMEDIATE
No. 1/34/1/2007-Cab.
GOVERNMENT OF INDIA (BHARAT SARKAR)
CABINET SECRETARIAT (MANTRIMANDAL SACHIVALAYA)
New Delhi, the 18th May, 2007
28 Vaisakha, 1929 (S)
The undersigned is directed to say that Smt. V. Radhika Selvi was
sworn in by the President as a Minister of State at 0930 hours on Friday, the
18th May, 2007, in the Rashtrapati Bhavan, New Delhi.
(K.L. Sharma)
for Cabinet Secretary
Tele : 2301 5802
All Members of the Council of Ministers.
Copy forwarded for information to Deputy Chairman and Members of the
Planning Commission.
(K.L. Sharma)
for Cabinet Secretary

Secretary to the President.
Secretary to the Vice-President.
(K.L. Sharma)

Copy also forwarded for information to :-
Principal Secretary to the Prime Minister.
(K.L. Sharma)
Deputy Secretary (Cabinet)
Copy forwarded to Secretary-General, Lok Sabha, Secretary-General,
Rajya Sabha, all Secretaries/Special Secretaries/ Additional Secretaries to the
Govt. of India/Chairman, Railway Board, for information.
(K.L. Sharma)
